.SH NAME
tty_hangup \- trigger a hangup event
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" tty_hangup
.BI "(struct tty_struct *tty "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "tty" 12
tty to hangup

A carrier loss (virtual or otherwise) has occurred on this like
schedule a hangup sequence to run after this event.
